column4: State UI Wage Records is the administrative data source of information used to collect employment and earnings-related data.
Wage Record Interchange System (WRIS II) is the administrative data source of information used to collect employment and earnings-related data.
Federal Employment Data Exchange System (FEDES) is the administrative data source of information used to collect employment and earnings-related data.
The administrative data source of information used to collect employment and earnings-related data is in a category not defined in CEDS.
